[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0239","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0682","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 SMTP 邮件中继安全绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 存在电子邮件中继绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可以利用封装的 SMTP 地址格式（如\"<user@domain.com>\"嵌入在邮件地址字段中）发送邮件，即使服务器已启用防中继功能，仍能绕过限制将邮件中继到外部域。该漏洞可被垃圾邮件发送者利用来发送大量垃圾邮件，导致服务器被滥用为开放中继。影响 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 版本，攻击无需认证，仅需构造特制邮件地址即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0682"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.280","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-027 提供的 Exchange Server 5.5 安全更新，该补丁使封装的 SMTP 地址同样受反中继保护。若无法安装补丁，可在 Internet Mail Service 属性中将中继权限限制为仅允许经过身份验证的用户，并禁用不必要的站点到站点 SMTP 中继功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237927","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-056.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/567","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-027"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0322","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0322.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0727","title":"OpenBSD 内核信息泄露导致 IPsec 数据包未加密发送漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 内核中存在一个信息泄露漏洞，由于内核在处理 IPsec（互联网协议安全）数据包时存在缺陷，导致某些情况下 IPsec 数据包可能以未加密的明文形式发送。攻击者可以利用此漏洞通过网络远程窃听敏感通信内容，获取本应受 IPsec 保护的机密信息。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 系统的机密性，攻击条件为能够拦截网络流量。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0727"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-06","updated":"2024-11-20","remediation":"升级 OpenBSD 系统到包含该漏洞修复的版本，或应用厂商发布的相关安全补丁。同时建议检查 IPsec 配置确保加密策略正确生效，并监控网络流量中是否存在未加密的 IPsec 数据包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T14:01:07.354663839+00:00","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6127","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0727"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0322.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0319","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0319.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0719","title":"Gnumeric Guile 插件代码执行漏洞","description":"Gnumeric 电子表格软件中的 Guile 插件存在代码执行漏洞。攻击者可通过诱使用户打开特制的恶意电子表格文件，利用 Guile 脚本扩展功能执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Gnumeric 的早期版本，攻击者需要本地访问权限或诱导用户下载并打开恶意文件，CVSS v2.0 评分为 4.6，可导致机密性、完整性和可用性部分受损。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0719"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.830","remediation":"升级 Gnumeric 至 1.2.x 以上版本，该漏洞在后续版本中已修复 Guile 插件对 Scheme 代码的沙箱逃逸问题。如无法升级，可移除或禁用 gnumeric-guile 插件包（如 Debian/Ubuntu 中执行 apt-get remove gnumeric-guile），或限制 Guile 插件仅加载受信任的 Scheme 脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/563"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0319.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1300","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1300.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0913","title":"Network Security Wizards Dragon-Fire IDS 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Dragon-Fire IDS 1.0 的 dfire.cgi 脚本存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 HTTP 请求参数中插入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）来执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 Network Security Wizards 公司出品的 Dragon-Fire IDS 1.0 版本，无需认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0913"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-05","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，建议禁用 dfire.cgi 脚本或限制其访问来源。如无法禁用，在 Web 服务器层面对所有用户输入过滤 shell 元字符（;|&`$），并配置防火墙仅允许可信 IP 访问 Dragon-Fire IDS 管理界面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93383593909438&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/564","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19444"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19444"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1300.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0285","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0285.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0703","title":"OpenBSD/BSDI等多款Unix操作系统设备文件标志设置漏洞","description":"OpenBSD、BSDI 及其他类 Unix 操作系统中，普通用户可对字符设备和块设备调用 chflags 及 fchflags 系统调用来修改文件标志位。该漏洞源于内核未对设备特殊文件的标志修改操作进行充分的权限检查，导致低权限用户能够更改设备文件的不可变标志（如 schg、sappnd），从而绕过系统安全策略。攻击者利用此漏洞可修改关键设备文件的保护属性，进而实现文件篡改或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD、BSDI 等多款 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 3.6，危害等级低，攻击需本地用户权限。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0703"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.917","remediation":"升级 OpenBSD 至 2.5 或更高版本，BSDI 升级至 4.0.1 或更高版本，该漏洞已在对应版本的内核中修复了对字符设备和块设备的 chflags/fchflags 权限检查。如无法升级，可通过限制用户对 /dev 目录下设备文件的写入权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-066.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0703.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0703","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0703.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0703.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r2hm-7w9p-5qrc/GHSA-r2hm-7w9p-5qrc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0703.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--397c3002-48f0-4b72-a230-03cbb311dac0.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000716.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0285.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0204","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0671","title":"ToxSoft NextFTP 1.82 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ToxSoft NextFTP 1.82 客户端存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务器发送特制的 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令，在客户端解析响应时触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 NextFTP 1.82 及更早版本，攻击者需诱导用户连接恶意 FTP 服务器即可触发，无需额外认证。CVSS v2 评分 5.1，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0671"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-08-03","updated":"1999-08-03","remediation":"该漏洞影响 ToxSoft NextFTP 1.82 及更早版本，厂商已停止维护且不再发布安全更新。建议立即停止使用 NextFTP，迁移至支持安全更新的替代 FTP 客户端（如 FileZilla、WinSCP）。如无法立即替换，可在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信 IP 访问 FTP 服务器，并在客户端侧禁用主动模式下的 CWD 命令预处理功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19448"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0224","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0224.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0677","title":"Ramp Networks WebRamp Web 管理默认口令漏洞","description":"WebRamp 200i 与 M3 网络设备的 Web 管理界面存在默认口令漏洞，设备出厂时预置了未强制修改的管理员默认密码。远程攻击者只需通过网络访问管理端口，使用默认凭据即可登录并获得设备完全管理权限，进而可修改网络配置、窃取通信数据或发起中间人攻击。该漏洞风险等级高，影响范围广泛，且利用难度极低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0677"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-03","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Ramp Networks WebRamp 200i/M3 路由器出厂预置默认管理员密码且未强制用户修改，攻击者可直接通过 Web 管理界面登录获取完全控制权。由于该产品已停止维护多年无安全更新，建议立即登录管理界面修改默认密码，在防火墙限制仅白名单 IP 可访问 Web 管理端口（80/443）；若设备仍在生产环境使用，应尽快替换为仍在安全支持周期内的替代产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/577","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0677"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0224.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0211","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0672","title":"Fujitsu Chocoa IRC 客户端远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R IRC 客户端存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的 IRC 频道主题（Topic）消息触发该漏洞，导致客户端崩溃或可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R 版本，攻击者只需控制 IRC 频道即可发起攻击，无需用户交互。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0672"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.990","remediation":"Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R 已停止维护，官方未发布安全更新。建议立即卸载 Fujitsu Chocoa，改用其他仍在维护的 IRC 客户端（如 HexChat、Irssi 等）。如无法卸载，可在防火墙规则中限制 IRC 端口（6660-6669/TCP）的出站连接作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/573","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19449","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e7c7f7ae9af22de7901413e757a1767cf5623277/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0672","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0672.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/307.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.223","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1053","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1053.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1337","title":"Midnight Commander FTP客户端历史文件敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Midnight Commander（mc）4.5.11 之前版本的 FTP 客户端存在敏感信息泄露漏洞。该客户端在访问 FTP 站点后，会将用户名和密码以明文形式存储于全局可读的历史记录文件中，导致本地其他用户可读取该文件获取凭证信息，进而实现权限提升。攻击者只需具备本地普通用户权限即可利用此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1337"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Midnight Commander 4.5.11 或更高版本，该版本已修复密码明文存储问题。如无法升级，立即执行 chmod 600 ~/.mc/history 限制历史文件权限为仅当前用户可读写，并删除该文件中已保存的明文密码条目。建议使用 .netrc 文件替代自动保存密码功能，并定期检查历史文件是否包含敏感信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93370073207984&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/9873.php","http://www.osvdb.org/5921","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1337"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1053.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0240","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0240.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0683","title":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 ICMP报文拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 在处理畸形的 ICMP 数据包时存在缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标防火墙发送特制的 ICMP 报文，触发服务崩溃导致拒绝服务。该漏洞直接影响 Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 版本，可造成安全防护中断、网络流量失去过滤，为后续攻击创造条件。利用方式简单，仅需发送构造的恶意 ICMP 数据包即可实现。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0683"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.410","remediation":"升级到 Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复畸形 ICMP 包处理逻辑。如无法升级，可在防火墙上配置 ICMP 包过滤规则，丢弃类型不明的 ICMP 报文作为临时缓解措施。鉴于产品已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的防火墙解决方案如 McAfee NGFW 或同类产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1029","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/556","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19441","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/122439703ba8729c2a612b649ea87112305b8e28/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0683","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0683.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3834-9q92-mj44/GHSA-3834-9q92-mj44.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/c77faccf7cf2fb75741042a2f81e7d733860667d/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0683.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0240.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0240.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0240.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0972","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1130","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server JHTML 文件源码泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1及3.6版本中搜索引擎的默认配置存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过构造特制的搜索请求，利用HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat模式文件读取服务器上JHTML文件的源代码，导致敏感信息（如数据库连接参数、业务逻辑配置等）泄露。该漏洞影响Netscape Enterprise Server多个版本，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1130"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.070","remediation":"Netscape Enterprise Server 已停止维护且不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 IIS）。作为临时缓解措施，可删除或重命名默认搜索配置中的 HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat 模式文件，并限制对搜索功能的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93346448121208&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93337389603117&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/559","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19443"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0972.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1014","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1227","title":"Ethereal 数据包捕获文件本地符号链接攻击任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Ethereal（现更名为 Wireshark）网络封包分析工具在保存捕获文件时未能正确处理符号链接（symlink），存在不安全的临时文件释放漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在目标系统上预设恶意的符号链接，诱使 Ethereal 进程将捕获数据写入攻击者指定的任意文件路径，从而覆盖系统关键文件或用户数据。该漏洞攻击条件简单，本地用户即可利用，影响所有使用 Ethereal 保存数据包捕获文件的场景，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1227"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.377","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 Ethereal 在写入数据包捕获文件时未检查符号链接，攻击者可提前创建指向任意系统文件的符号链接，诱使 Ethereal 覆盖目标文件。建议立即升级至 Ethereal 0.8.0 或更高版本（该版本已修复符号链接跟随问题），或直接迁移至 Wireshark（Ethereal 的更名后继项目，默认不存在此漏洞）。临时缓解措施：避免以 root 权限运行 Ethereal，将捕获文件输出到专用目录并确保该目录不允许非信任用户写入，同时设置严格的 umask 限制文件权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ethereal.com/lists/ethereal-dev/199907/msg00126.html","http://www.ethereal.com/lists/ethereal-dev/199907/msg00130.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3334","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1227","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1227.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fx42-9wp5-842h/GHSA-fx42-9wp5-842h.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87548/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000713.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0276","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0276.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0700","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 电话拨号程序缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的电话拨号程序（dialer.exe）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞（CWE-119）。当系统加载包含特制畸形拨号条目的 dialer.ini 配置文件时，拨号程序在处理该条目过程中发生缓冲区溢出，攻击者可借此在系统上下文中执行任意代码。该漏洞影响安装了 SP1 至 SP5 的所有 Windows NT 4.0 版本，CVSS 2.0 评分为 6.2（MEDIUM，向量：AV:L/AC:H/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C）。利用该漏洞需要本地访问权限，攻击者必须能够修改或向目标系统写入恶意的 dialer.ini 文件，然后触发拨号程序加载该配置文件。成功利用可导致攻击者完全控制受影响系统，获得系统级权限。Microsoft 已于 1999 年 7 月通过安全公告 MS99-026 及知识库文章 KB237185 发布修复补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0700"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.550","remediation":"Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2019+ 等受支持版本。如无法升级，在 dialer.ini 中移除可疑条目，限制 dialer.exe 执行权限，并禁用 Phone Dialer 服务作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237185","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-026","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19440","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2f8583cd0e244c401900c481a78c07fe5535c09f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0700","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0700.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/808b57c97f3c3a63ccc1ba2e5715700b4df9d9e8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-256c-v65p-vvfh/GHSA-256c-v65p-vvfh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9d37c81c-28be-4e85-a09d-7f39454834f2.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0276.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0492","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0492.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0770","title":"Check Point Firewall-1 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Check Point Software Firewall-1 存在连接超时设置缺陷，防火墙对以 ACK 等非 SYN 标志位开头的连接设置了过长的超时时间，导致攻击者可通过向无响应的目标系统发起大量此类连接请求，使防火墙连接表被迅速填满而饱和，从而耗尽系统资源，造成防火墙服务崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Firewall-1 3.0 及 4.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级低但利用方式简单。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0770"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.327","remediation":"升级 Check Point Firewall-1 至 4.1 及以上版本，该版本修复了非 SYN 报文超时过长的问题。如无法升级，在防火墙规则中设置连接速率限制，并将非 SYN 连接的超时时间缩短至 30 秒以下，同时配置 SYN 代理（SYN Defender）以过滤非正常握手包，缓解表耗尽攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1027","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/549","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19436"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0492.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0924","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0924.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1078","title":"WS_FTP Pro 配置文件口令弱加密漏洞","description":"WS_FTP Pro 6.0 在初始化文件 ws_ftp.ini 中采用弱加密算法存储用户口令，攻击者在获取该配置文件后即可轻易解密出明文口令，进而获取系统登录权限。该漏洞利用难度较低，无需特殊权限即可利用，对受影响系统的机密性和完整性构成严重威胁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1078"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.527","remediation":"升级 WS_FTP Pro 至 6.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复密码弱加密问题；鉴于 WS_FTP Pro 已停止维护且不再有安全更新，建议迁移至支持现代安全凭据存储的 FTP/SFTP 客户端（如 FileZilla 或 WinSCP），避免在配置文件中以任何形式明文或弱加密保存密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9907&L=ntbugtraq&D=0&P=10370&F=P","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/547","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1078","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1078.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0924.toml"}]